text:
Stadium Avenue, west side, at the head of Polo Place, as seen from the latter.

May 19, 1938.

P. L. Sperr.

(1) Traveling Library: This library on wheels, operated by the Extension Division of the New York Public Library, is seen at the Holy Angels School of the New York Catholic Protectory, on Unionport Road, in the Bronx.

May 10, 1938.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) Another stop on Stadium Ave., at Polo Place.

May 19, 1938.

P. L. Sperr.

(3) Farther north in the borough, on Fenton Ave., at Knapp Street.

May 11, 1938.

P. L. Sperr.
